                Farida Orujova · Operations Director
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-slide w-full flex-shrink-0">
              <blockquote class="text-2xl sm:text-[28px] font-semibold text-brand-text dark:text-brand-text-dark leading-relaxed" data-i18n="testimonials.card2.quote">
                “Our managers finally have one source of truth. Prep boards, POS, and analytics update as fast as service moves.”
              </blockquote>
              <p class="mt-6 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-cta-text dark:text-brand-cta-text-dark" data-i18n="testimonials.card2.author">
                Ahmed Hassan · Multi-unit Owner
