                Maria Rodriguez · Beverage Lead
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-slide w-full flex-shrink-0">
              <blockquote class="text-2xl sm:text-[28px] font-semibold text-brand-text dark:text-brand-text-dark leading-relaxed" data-i18n="testimonials.card4.quote">
                “Because KDSX automates routing and reporting, we redeployed two full-time ops roles to guest experience.”
              </blockquote>
              <p class="mt-6 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-cta-text dark:text-brand-cta-text-dark" data-i18n="testimonials.card4.author">
